# Rust
/target/
**/*.rs.bk

# proptest writes a regression seed file whenever a property test fails. In
# this repo's TDD workflow the deliberately-failing red-phase stub generates
# meaningless seeds; real counterexamples surface as CI failures and are fixed
# with targeted tests. Not tracked (matches the repo's established state).
**/proptest-regressions/

